<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sluttish" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Sluttish,</orth> unclean, nasty: <bibl n="shak. ven 983" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 983</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 55.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 55, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 5.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 90</bibl>. In a moral sense: <cit><quote>s. spoils of opportunity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 62</bibl></cit> (cf. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 134</bibl>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>